oai_dc:dc.dc:title: First Volume of the Proceedings of the Twenty-Fifth Annual Conference (1992). World Association for Buiatrics President's Welcome
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Espinasse, J.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This year the XVII World Buiatrics Congress is being organized by the American Association of Bovine Practitioners at Saint Paul, Minnesota USA (August 31st - September 4th, 1992). It is to be combined with the XXV American Association of Bovine Practitioner's Conference. PDF contains translations of the speech in French, Spanish, and German.
